slivrosminha bibliotecaajudapesquisa de livros avançadaver elivroobter este livro em versão impressaamazoncombarnesnoblecombooksamillionindieboundencontrar em uma bibliotecatodos os vendedores »economic control of quality of manufactures productth anniversary commemorative issueno volume walter andrew shewhartasq press    páginas  resenhahttpsbooksgooglecombooksabouteconomiccontrolofqualityofmanufactuhtmlhlptbrideoynralpocwhen walter a shewhart the father of modern quality control described his book asan indication of the direction in which future developments may be expected to take place could he have forseen its enormous impact this monumental work laid the foundation for this modern quality control discipline and it remains as current today as ever it began as an attempt to develop a scientific basis for attaining economic control of quality through the establishment of control limits to indicate when the quality of product is varying more than is economically desirable in his search for better knowledge of economy in manufacture shewhart touches upon all aspects of statistical quality control the book includes a presentation of the fundamental concepts and advantages of statistical control ways of expressing quality of product a section containing a discourse that has been described as a masterpiece on the meaning of quality the basis for specification of quality control sampling fluctuations in quality allowable variability in quality which contains the first fully developed use of control charts and quality control in practice this is required reading for anyone seriously interested in the study of quality control about the author the father of modern quality control walter a shewhart brought together the disciplines of statistics engineering and economics in a simple but highly effective tool the control chart this technique and the principles behind it have played key roles in economic developments from the s through to the present day most of shewharts professional career was spent at western electric as an engineer from  to  and at bell telephone laboratories from  until his retirement in  in addition he served for more than  years as the first editor of the mathematical statistics series published by john wiley  sons o que estão dizendo  escrever uma resenhanão encontramos nenhuma resenha nos lugares comunsoutras edições  visualizar todoseconomic control of quality of manufactured productwalter andrew shewhartvisualização parcial  economic control of quality of manufactured productwalter andrew shewhartvisualização de trechos  economic control of quality of manufactured productwalter a shewhartnão há visualização disponível  referências a este livrostatistical methods for environmental pollution monitoringrichard o gilbertvisualização parcial  managing quality the strategic and competitive edgedavid a garvinvisualização parcial  todos os resultados da pesquisa de livros raquo informações bibliográficastítuloeconomic control of quality of manufactures productth anniversary commemorative issueno volume autorwalter andrew shewhartediçãoreimpressão reediçãoeditoraasq press isbn num págs páginasnbspnbspexportar citaçãobibtex endnote refmansobre o google livros  política de privacidade  termos de serviço  informações para editoras  informar um problema  ajuda  sitemap  página inicial do googleeconomic control of quality of manufactured product  walter andrew shewhart  google booksmy accountsearchmapsyoutubeplaynewsgmaildrivecalendargoogletranslatephotosmoreshoppingwalletfinancedocsbooksbloggercontactshangoutskeepeven more from googlesign inhidden fieldsbooksbooksgooglecomhttpsbooksgooglecombooksabouteconomiccontrolofqualityofmanufactuhtmlidjtvnaaaamaajutmsourcegbgplusshareeconomic control of quality of manufactured productmy libraryhelpadvanced book searchview ebookget this book in printabebooksamazonfind in a libraryall sellers »economic control of quality of manufactured productwalter andrew shewhartd van nostrand comp